{"type":"article","id":17241,"title":"「哀悼日」，中共官媒怎么处理习近平照片（图集）","uid":3685,"topics":[934,120,136,455,5262],"contents":"(1/?)<br>\n研究一下中国官方网站和媒体是怎么处理今天的黑白默哀：<br>\n外交部：黑白与彩色混搭，仅习李照片彩色；<br>\n人民日报：头版中习与诸领导人植树照片彩色，其余黑色；<br>\n新华网：无习照片；<br>\n人民网；无习照片；&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nhttps://t.co/xxmgRNTvRC<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHK_VUMAAc_hB?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHK_VUMAAc_hB?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHK_VUMAAc_hB?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHLz5UEAEv3MX?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHLz5UEAEv3MX?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHLz5UEAEv3MX?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHMPtUYAYZmQ6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHMPtUYAYZmQ6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHMPtUYAYZmQ6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n(2/?)<br>\n环球网：无习照片；<br>\n中国共青团：无习照片；<br>\n中青网：无习照片；<br>\n中国军网：无习照片；<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOFhUEAA_je6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOFhUEAA_je6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOFhUEAA_je6?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOtfU8AU6N_C?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOtfU8AU6N_C?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHOtfU8AU6N_C?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHPh4UUAAdSs7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHPh4UUAAdSs7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHPh4UUAAdSs7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHQR_UUAAA8tn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHQR_UUAAA8tn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHQR_UUAAA8tn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHNKSUMAAqpp2?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHNKSUMAAqpp2?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHNKSUMAAqpp2?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n(3/?)<br>\n央视网：无习照片；<br>\n央广网：无习照片；<br>\n学习强国：包括他在内全黑白；<br>\nChina Daily：包括他在内全黑白；<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRHcU8AAhRi5?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRHcU8AAhRi5?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRHcU8AAhRi5?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRz9UMAEj-zU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRz9UMAEj-zU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHRz9UMAEj-zU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHSsqUEAEDdrL?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHSsqUEAEDdrL?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHSsqUEAEDdrL?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHTWQUUAACaRS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHTWQUUAACaRS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHTWQUUAACaRS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n(4/?)<br>\n中国政府网：包括习植树照片在内的头版照片均为全彩，其余黑白；<br>\n中共新闻网：全彩，一点哀悼气息都看不到，相关字眼都没有。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHU0UVAAI4ryD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHU0UVAAI4ryD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHU0UVAAI4ryD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHWTiUUAAMSHi?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHWTiUUAAMSHi?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EUuHWTiUUAAMSHi?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n(5/?)<br>\n虽然几乎所有网站都刻意从首页撤下了习的照片以避免出现其黑白像，但头条均是他参加植树活动的报道，只打一行字在最顶端。<br>\n如果打开手机版页面，更能看出不同——所有新闻里只有与习有关的没有预览图。<br>\n<br>\n举国哀悼，不过仍有人光鲜亮丽。","date":"2020-04-05","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":0}